  "description": "A weathered, vintage mechanical meter stands prominently in the foreground, surrounded by lush greenery. The meter is cylindrical with a white face displaying a gauge, and it's mounted on a turquoise base with visible rust and aging. The meter is framed by a white picket fence and dense foliage in shades of green and reddish-brown. In the background, a stone monument with a statue atop is visible, suggesting a park or memorial setting. The overall scene is slightly overcast with soft light, creating a muted color palette.",
